verbose_text: Macrophages generate several profibrotic factors, including galectin-3, transforming growth factor (TGF)-beta, insulin like growth factor-1, platelet derived growth factor and basic fibroblast growth factor, which support the generation, survival and proliferation of myofibroblasts, and drive tissue fibrosis.
